      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GUS THE JET (4) crossed from out wide chasing down the leaders to score by 4.5 lengths (20.00) at Capalaba in Grade 5 over 366m. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Can make it two on the bounce. RITZA LAW (8) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 2.25 lengths away in third (25.34) at Grafton in a NG over 450m. Has won two of three starts from this draw. Will give a great sight again. KOBY KEEPING (7) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (25.40) at this track. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can feature again. LUCKY TIME (3) produced a speedy 19.84 when filling a minor placing last start. Can measure up with a repeat.",
